# Browser "Save as Complete Webpage" bundles — not production content
# Chrome saves an HTML file + a *_files/ folder with CSS/JS/UI images.
# These are design reference sessions accidentally placed in walkthroughs/.
# NOTE: actual evidence screenshots (.webp/.jpg/.png) in the same directory
# are NOT ignored and will continue to be tracked normally.
public/media/walkthroughs/**/*_files/
public/media/walkthroughs/**/*.html
